data.description: Welcome to South Deering, where we present a fantastic opportunity to own a charming brick ranch-style home! This 3-bedroom, 1-bath residence offers a comfortable and inviting living space, complemented by desirable features and a convenient location. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet evenings with your loved ones. The kitchen boasts a generous amount of space, complete with a table area, providing the ideal spot for family meals or casual dining. One of the standout features of this home is the back addition, which encompasses a large family room and a wood-burning fireplace. Imagine cozying up in front of the crackling fire during chilly evenings or using this versatile space for gatherings and relaxation.  Step outside, and you'll discover a nice-sized backyard that beckons you to enjoy the outdoors. The detached two-car garage provides ample space for parking and storage, while a concrete patio offers an inviting area for outdoor dining, barbecues, or simply unwinding in the fresh air. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this delightful brick ranch-style home in South Deering. Property in great location, close to public transportation to the Loop. Great option for clients looking for a ranch with no interior steps.  Schedule a viewing today and envision yourself settling into this comfortable and welcoming residence. Your dream of homeownership awaits!
